tmed_7=ts(tmed_mes$julio,start = 1981,frequency = 1)

p_tmed_1=autoplot(tmed_1)+xlab("Año")+ylab("Temperatura media [°C]")+ggtitle("Temperatura media C1 - Cundinamarca del mes: Enero",subtitle = "Periodo 1981-2020 Fase: Senescencia y Cosecha")+ geom_line(aes(y=tmed_1,colour="T. media °C"))  + geom_line(aes(y=10,colour="T. limite °C"))+ scale_colour_manual("", values=c("T. media °C"="black", "T. limite °C"="red"))
